# CONFIDENTIAL: P.V.T Station Project

Dear Team Member,

As requested, here is the code snippet for the P.V.T Station proximity sensor system. Please implement this in the Arduino controller as soon as possible.

**IMPORTANT NOTICE:**
Head to the P.V.T Station to retrieve the code you need.
(⚠️: KEEP AN EYE ON THE DISTANCE)

```cpp
if (distance = 15) {
   Serial.println("Color1: ------");
   setColor(//color1);
} 

else if (distance = 35) {
   Serial.println("Color2: -----");
   setColor(//color2);
} 

else if (distance = 50) {
   Serial.println("Color3: -----");
   setColor(//color3);
} 

else {
   Serial.println("Color: Off");
   setColor(0, 0, 0);
}
```

Please note that the color values need to be determined based on the calibration of the specific sensor unit. The distance values (15, 35, 50) are in centimeters and should not be modified.

Let me know if you have any questions about the implementation.

Regards,

